He exhorted (people) to take arms to make a change,'' Carlos Ortiz
Ramirez, political secretary of Stroessner's Colorado Party, said
in a July 20 interview.
   ``Corrective measures are going to be taken in this case ... We
cannot permit a foreigner to get involved in our affairs.''
