<TEXT>
   A bomb exploded early today in an empty
lot near the South African Embassy, causing minor damage to the
building, an embassy spokesman said.
   Marius Louw said the bomb went off at about 6:30 a.m., smashing
windows and damaging a wall of the embassy, which is located in a
